Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 旭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少还是挺强壮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盐就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明大人会守护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 我承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会来接你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来得教育一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果 这个世界上有恶魔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想 一定就是这个样子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是还平安无事的活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定得找到盐
